# ── AI Development Tools ────────────────────────────────────
# .gemini/ workspace cruft is ignored; the GitHub App's repo-level config
# (.gemini/config.yaml) and optional styleguide.md are tracked so review
# policy lives in the repo.
.gemini/*
!.gemini/config.yaml
!.gemini/styleguide.md
.agent/
.development-archive/
_bmad/
_bmad-output/
CLAUDE.local.md
# ── Claude Code ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# CLAUDE.md is tracked — it's the primary AI context file for the project.
# .claude/ contains local settings (API keys, permissions) — never shared.
# EXCEPTION: .claude/rules/ ships with the repo — it is auto-loaded by the
# .claude/rules/ contract (Anthropic memory docs). The /* form below lets the
# negation re-include the rules subdirectory; git cannot re-include children
# of a fully excluded parent.
.claude/*
!.claude/rules/
!.claude/settings.json

# ── SpecifyKit ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Dev specs/plans generated locally, not shipped with product.
.specify/

# ── Internal Dev Artifacts ───────────────────────────────────
# Development research, specs, and prompts — tracked for backup.
# plans/
# specs/
# docs/prompts/
# docs/plans/

# ── Husky Internals (only .husky/pre-commit is tracked) ────
.husky/_/

# ── Project-Specific: Ephemeral Dev Artifacts ───────────────
# One-off scripts generated during dev sessions (root-only)
/claude-*.sh
/test-*.sh
/test-*.js
/test-*.cjs
/test-*.html

# Generated reports
audit-report.json
css-integrity-baselines.json
css-integrity-report.json
eslint_*.json
page_eslint_results.json
hooks.json

# Legacy one-off CJS scripts (root-only)
/check_eslint.cjs
/quick_eslint_count.cjs
/simple_validate.cjs
/validate_mission_control.cjs

# Build framework generated reports
tests/visual/pi-baseline-report.json

# Autotools artifacts (root-only)
/ltmain.sh

# Debug/test utilities (not part of main app)
utils/debug/
utils/python/

# Console debug output
console.debug.txt
console.debug.*

